  m_text: 'Apart from wall running horrizontally and upwards you can wall run downwards

    Try
    jumping towards this wall then turning your back on it while holding forwards

    You
    can slow your ruyn down by pressing backwards(S) in this state

    Then jump
    of the wall to lanmd on the platform

'
